  AUTHORS
  =======

  This is a list of authors who have written
  or edited parts of the ntop sources.


  o Original author of ntop:
    Luca Deri <deri at ntop.org>



  CONTRIBUTORS
  ============
  o Rocco Carbone <rocco at ntop.org>
    starting at version 1.2.13a he wrote the NtoPerl Module
    and adapted the configuration stuff to use GNU auto{make,conf}

